Package fr.upmc.datacenter.software.interfaces

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    RequestI
    The interface RequestI must be implemented by requests submitted to a TaskDispatcher for execution as a job for an application running on the data center.
    RequestNotificationHandlerI
    The interface RequestNotificationHandlerI defines the methods that must be implemented by a component to handle request notifications received through an inboud port RequestNotificationInboundPort.
    RequestNotificationI
    The interface RequestNotificationI defines the notification of request termination.
    RequestSubmissionHandlerI
    The interface RequestSubmissionHandlerI defines the component internal services to receive and execute requests.
    RequestSubmissionI
    The interface RequestSubmissionI defines the component services to receive and execute requests.
